      "translation": "(1) For Ninĝirsu , the powerful warrior of Enlil , his master , Ur-Ningirsu , ruler of Lagaš , son of Gudea , ruler of Lagaš , the builder of Ninĝirsu's E-ninnu , made the temple of Nanše adjacent to the gate of honest speech ."
